headline: Oppenheimer Remains Positive on Costco (COST), Names it a ‘Top Pick’
summary: Costco Wholesale Corporation (NASDAQ:COST) is one of the best dividend stocks to buy. On November 6, Costco announced a comparable sales growth in October of 6.7%, up from 5.7% the prior month.
